{"word":"H2336 - חֹוחַ - chôwach - kho'-akh - Bramble","slug":"H2336","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חֹוחַ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>chôwach"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kho'-akh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bramble"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D7;&#x05D5;&#x05D7; - cho&#x0302;ach</b> - <i>kho'-akh</i><p/>From an unused root apparently meaning to <i>pierce</i>; a <i>thorn</i>; by analogy a <i>ring</i> for the nose: - bramble, thistle, thorn."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2337\">H2337</a>, <a href=\"#/H2397\">H2397</a>"}]}